ROBLEE v. BARSS. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. March 1, 1894.) Action by Hiram O. Roblee against William Barss.

Argued before MAYHAM, P. J., and HERRICK and PUTNAM, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for leave to go to court of appeals denied, with $10 costs. See 26 N. Y. Supp. 461.
